{"tid":92641,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個散心好去處","createTime":"2017-01-23T17:24:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-24T06:30:33.000Z","uid":9031,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0dad6bdac0e597d3c464dd105fcfc8e8d85041a8","tid":92641,"uid":9031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T17:24:49.000Z","msg":"唔知各位有冇相同興趣，鐘意一個人去散心<br />\n我先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n閒日大尾篤堤壩，十二點過後自己踩單車入，有星星、海風、又寧靜，帶一個藍芽音響聽自己鍾意既音樂，加啤酒放鬆心情冇得輸，咩壓力都冇曬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/24/012353_caf6b32291d5ad3edb817cf4a4e09c15.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F24%2F012353_caf6b32291d5ad3edb817cf4a4e09c15.jpg&h=331371a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n純粹分享下都市人減壓方法，手下留情 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fc7b66cf869a64df36e399fedf005426046ecea","tid":92641,"uid":40949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T17:49:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />飲咗酒揸單車係犯法的"},{"pid":"8cebfe6c35b31380bea945f1ed278ae39979d751","tid":92641,"uid":40949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T17:53:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />飲咗酒揸單車係犯法的</blockquote><br />\nBTW，小弟覺得行山非常正，香港風景好靚<br />\n當然唔係鳩假期石屎路啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a39ad5d5cdc0b910b030f1fbf72f8fce1f55752f","tid":92641,"uid":9031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T17:59:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />飲咗酒揸單車係犯法的</blockquote><br />\n飲少少hea陣就冇事 <br />\n最緊要記得目的係放鬆 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16ba8cfe64f4b79f1249ac9ee41a1bed10cb30ed","tid":92641,"uid":9031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T18:00:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />飲咗酒揸單車係犯法的</blockquote><br />\nBTW，小弟覺得行山非常正，香港風景好靚<br />\n當然唔係鳩假期石屎路啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係好正，不過真係好攰唔係人人頂到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"374e809d6cff7b790eaac36ed73994fd3ec542a0","tid":92641,"uid":10620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T18:02:17.000Z","msg":"其實好想好似樓主咁去呢啲地方散心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但覺得太靜會危險"},{"pid":"3b8376c4b45971a951353e8a32983cb1eaa2ab95","tid":92641,"uid":7762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T18:03:15.000Z","msg":"上天文台嗰邊睇星星都好正"},{"pid":"700310b68ec020222e52574d901d66533b7c376f","tid":92641,"uid":58412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T18:05:18.000Z","msg":"釣魚都ok 吹下海風 靜候魚兒上釣嘅時候 又可以諗下野 睇下船 睇下對岸景色"},{"pid":"f93ae5df81e0af820d074ff157217e375c39debf","tid":92641,"uid":9031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T18:12:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實好想好似樓主咁去呢啲地方散心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但覺得太靜會危險</blockquote><br />\n危唔危險在乎當時心情，假若你好享受的話，你反而會好感恩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2349d850ca6d7f6918a1c975e0b1aea2e9bf972","tid":92641,"uid":10620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T18:17:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實好想好似樓主咁去呢啲地方散心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但覺得太靜會危險</blockquote><br />\n危唔危險在乎當時心情，假若你好享受的話，你反而會好感恩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我覺得唔危險嘅時候我嗰陣應該係絕望到想死<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fdec17059cd75adabf73c10c6cd8d94ef3099f4","tid":92641,"uid":33749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T18:18:11.000Z","msg":"見樓主踩單車<br />\n我間唔中會踩去羅湖站河對面嗰個警崗度<br />\n六七點踩過去<br />\n梧桐河定雙魚河隔離踩都幾舒服<br />\n係夏天多蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0724dff66881fd15c19f8215d96a036e9f15a7c5","tid":92641,"uid":33749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T18:19:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實好想好似樓主咁去呢啲地方散心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但覺得太靜會危險</blockquote><br />\n危唔危險在乎當時心情，假若你好享受的話，你反而會好感恩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我覺得唔危險嘅時候我嗰陣應該係絕望到想死<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n香港其實算好安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大把人行夜山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過上年年尾先有單大陸人日光日白喺郊野公園老笠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b02696cb7ac5994880deb7bc8fe33534539b3a85","tid":92641,"uid":9031,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T18:22:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實好想好似樓主咁去呢啲地方散心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但覺得太靜會危險</blockquote><br />\n危唔危險在乎當時心情，假若你好享受的話，你反而會好感恩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我覺得唔危險嘅時候我嗰陣應該係絕望到想死<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔好被恐懼去支配自己，大不了咪死！<br />\n然後再充滿熱血地去冒險，就算死嘅話你都可以解脫，唔死都可以充份運用你條命去進行冒險，享受其中樂趣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad6bf8d764ae9f114a0d6e7cde1f1df359edda8a","tid":92641,"uid":76105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T06:30:33.000Z","msg":"一個人去咪仲孤單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}